lo. La antología de textos ensayísticos complementa el estudio y busca difundir los veintiséis textos primarios que constituyen el volumen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Spanish, Castilian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aPeruvian literaturexWomen authors2DLC. 0aPeruvian prose literaturey19th century2DLC. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Caribbean & Latin American.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.31819/978396869292040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783968692920423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783968692920/original  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles